- "Residence statuses" can be seen as the legal and social standing of a resident, reflecting their legal presence in the community;
- "Contact details" can be seen as the ways to reach out to a resident, symbolizing their connections to the outside world;
- "Audit trails" can be seen as the historical records of changes, documenting the evolution of their information over time.

sql:
